---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="解决方案 - Moxin Org">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-20 animate-fade-in">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-text-primary">您的 AI，您的基础设施</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        在您自己的服务器上部署完整的 Moxin 堆栈。完全隐私，零数据外流，以及企业级安全性。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-text-primary">私有化部署</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          我们在您的私有云或本地硬件上部署整个生态系统（MoFa, Moly）。
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-primary">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 font-bold text-xs">✓</div>
            <span>支持物理隔离安装</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-primary">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 font-bold text-xs">✓</div>
            <span>SSO & RBAC 集成</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-primary">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 font-bold text-xs">✓</div>
            <span>定制 SLA & 支持</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- <button class="w-full bg-text-primary text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-black transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-black/20">
          联系销售
        </button> -->
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">定制语音克隆</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            使用我们的 SFT（监督微调）管道克隆您高管的声音或创建独特的品牌声音。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">行业特定智能体</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            针对编码、客户支持和法律分析的预配置智能体集群。
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-text-primary">硬件咨询</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            关于使用消费级 GPU 构建最具成本效益的推理集群的专家建议。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>